the public `withdraw` entrypoint when residual gateway allowance remains."},{"title":"GatewayTransferNative claimRefund reads storage after delete risking zero amount","source_agents":["opencode_1"],"reason":"Duplicate of F-025; incorporated by adding `opencode_1` as supporting source for the existing event-integrity finding."}]}
